: Gonocoxite as 
<figureCitation box="[581,659,457,481]" captionStart="Figs 30-38" captionStartId="14.[332,370,1678,1697]" captionTargetBox="[375,1245,400,1648]" captionTargetId="figure-104@14.[355,1257,390,1658]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Figs 30-38. 30  Bironium ornatum sp. nov.: gonocoxite, scale = 0.05 mm. 3136, Bironium punctatum sp. nov.: 31, 32  Aedeagus in dorsal and lateral views, scale = 0.2 mm; 33  Tip of median lobe, scale = 0.05 mm; 34  Internal sac, scale = 0.05 mm; 35  Paramere in ventral view, scale = 0.1 mm; 36  Gonocoxite, scale = 0.05 mm. 3738, Bironium riedeli sp. nov.: Aedeagus in dorsal and lateral views, scale = 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5706185" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5706185/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="239">Fig. 30</figureCitation>
